methods.fromChunk:
Produce a TreeIndexImpl from a slice of a LongChunk of Attributes.OrderedKeyIndices.

:param keys: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.LongChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.OrderedKeyIndices>) - The LongChunk of Attributes.OrderedKeyIndices to build from
:param offset: (int) - The offset in keys to begin building from
:param length: (int) - The number of keys to include
:param disposable: boolean
:return: (io.deephaven.db.v2.utils.TreeIndexImpl) A new TreeIndexImpl containing the specified slice of keys
